               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Māḥleta ṣǝge "Canticle of the Flower" (fols. 1r-53v)
 II) Ṣalot
                     za-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝnä Māryām ba-Dabra Golgota, Prayer of Our Lady Mary on Mount
                     Golgotha on the 21st of Sane (fols. 54r-87v) (s. EMML 706-1; MHG-010/VII;
                     SDM-023)
 III) O-rǝḫrǝḫta ḫǝllinā... “O tender-hearted...” (fols. 87v-89v)
                     (ChRep no. 368)
 IV) Maṣḥafa kidāna mǝḥrat “Book of the Covenant of Mercy”
                     (fols. 90r-99v) (s. GKM-020)
 V) Malkǝʾa Krǝstos "Image of Christ" (fols.
                     99v-114r) (ChRep no. 295)
 VI Malkǝʾa Māryām "Image of Mary" (fols.
                     114r-119v), incomplete (ChRep no. 221)</summary>
